Subject: Deploy Print Screen and Snipping tool restriction
Description: Currently i am trying to deploy the feature of disable print screen and snipping tool however i can't make it work. I am enabling it through Content Aware Protection.
Solution_Comment__c:
Issue has been fixed by to the denylist the following :

Snippingtool.exe
ScreenSketch.exe 
ScreenClippingHost.exe
GameBar.exe 

All with the * parameter
